<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ wǒ zǒng shì ràng nǐ shāng xīn, qiú nǐ jīn rì lián mǐn wǒ,
 méi yǒu tīng nǐ de jiào dǎo, zhè shì wǒ de guò cuò,
 wǒ réng yào xiàng nǐ qí qiú, yòng nǐ dà néng shǒu chān fú wǒ,
 bù zài zǒu zì jǐ de lù, wán quán ràng nǐ dài lǐng wǒ.</lyrics>
